data.description: Welcome to Salt Lake!  Original Owner and well maintained with upgrades to see.  Prime location, minutes to Tripler, Shafter, Joint Base Pearl Harbor and easy highway access.  Remodeled kitchen with upgraded cabinetry, full-size washer/dryer, window A/C, newly installed upgraded window jealousies throughout.  Two full baths have been renovated.  This corner unit is with wall windows located at cool side of building.  Moanalua High School is a stone throw away!
